class  ConstraintProduct
 Interface for specifying user-defined evaluations of constraint products. More...

Detailed Description

Author:
Hans Joachim Ferreau, Andreas Potschka, Christian Kirches
Version:
3.0beta
Date:
2009-2012

Declaration of the ConstraintProduct class which allows to specify a user-defined function for evaluating the constraint product at the current iterate to speed-up QP solution in case of a specially structured constraint matrix.
